high_descs: Walk to the counter then take a step to your right.
Look up and open the cupboard all the way to the right and grab the orange cup that's up there then close the door.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the wall then turn right to face the microwave.
Look up and open the cupboard all the way to the left and put the cup up there and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the cupboard.

high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the kitchen, but align your self with the right side of the kitchen counter up ahead, then look up at the cupboards above the kitchen counter space
grab a cup out of the cupboard above the kitchen counter there
turn around and walk to the fridge at the end of the room on the left
place the cup inside the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the microwave in the left far corner of the end of the room
place the cup inside the cupboard above the microwave on the left
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved cup inside the cupboard to the top left of the microwave

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the right end of the counter.
Look up and take the gold glass out of the top right cabinet.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Place the glass on the top shelf of the fridge, to the right of the tomato. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and veer all the way left to the microwave.
Place the glass in the bottom shelf of the top left cabinet above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass in a cabinet.
